snippet.title: Conflict FPS Game Trailer May 2023
snippet.description:
Conflict FPS is a strategic first-person shooter focused on multip player combat. This video is a trailer introducing the game to prospective players while the free-to-play game is available for public playtesting on Steam.

With three playable battlegrounds and several weapons ready to play, we are happy to show you the work so far. If you want to become a playtester, please visit our Steam page and install the game.

Official site: https://conflictfps.com/
